{
  "stem": "22889.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Hujowa [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So used to kill the people, used to lay them down there, cover them up with stones, every day, every day until the hill was filled up, level.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they start on the other hill, Hujowa Gorka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one time I was assigned to bury people, me and few friends of mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I buried the people, and all of a sudden-- this was the worst thing happen to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It changed my life completely after this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I see my aunt and my cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought them in from outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody recognized them, and they were captured.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they brought them, and they killed them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't, I couldn't come to myself after this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so depressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't care what happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the worst thing because I buried other people who would-- didn't mean a thing, because people were killed every day, but it's different when you have to bury your own.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The way they went-- I never forget that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't want to even talk about it for years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was, was very hard on me to see my aunt-- you know, the way she was killed-- and my cousins.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, as long as you were in the camp, you got harder, harder.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You got stronger, stronger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had a will to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always want to live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SIGHS] In the camp-- life was very hard in Plaszow because you have to put up not only so much with the outside, the Ukrainians, also with the Jewish police, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes they were worse than the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
